#  Description:
#    Conversion file from Polish CSK to Polish Code Page Mazovia
#    Registry value (Decimal):  From 57383 to 57384
#    Registry value (Hex): From e027 to e028
#
#    This conversion uses enforced subset criteria-all unmappable characters
#    are mapped to the SUB character \x7f and lossy conversion error
#    is generated.
#
